  m_text: "hey, it\u2019s me.\r\nI just stepped off the train.\r\nthe first snow
    is falling,\r\nbut I was hoping for rain.\r\n\r\nthe train leaves in 15 minutes.\r\nI\u2019ll
    reach her in 20.\r\n\r\nthe first to arrive,\r\na whole night ahead of me.\r\n\r\nI
    hope she\u2019ll be good company."
